  <PlantBlazebulb.label>焰球罂粟</PlantBlazebulb.label>
  <!-- EN: Genetically engineered plant designed to yield pyrophoric compounds for use in incendiary weapons.\n\nGreat care must be taken in cultivating these as the incendiary compounds inside the bulbs can self-ignite at temperatures above 28°C/82F, requiring constant cooling to maintain optimal growth temperatures. -->
  <PlantBlazebulb.description>为了获得制作燃烧武器的燃烧剂而培育的转基因植物，培育时必须非常小心，球根中含有的可燃物甚至能在室温中自燃，需要保持一个阴凉的环境。</PlantBlazebulb.description>
  
